items.title: guide 1:
items.guide: Welcome to the breach guide, it will help you to know everything about the breach game. You will find many tips and tutorials. Also, in this guide, you will find out how to complete all levels of security breach in the easiest way.

items.title: guide 2:
items.guide: In a security breach, you must distract the enemies by knocking down paint cans and the toys escape before the enemies get close to your location. Jump into hiding and allow danger to pass, or try to escape from your pursuers. Security Breaches Game Guide contains many useful hidden secrets and many more to break down all the stages and missions of this game to use to your advantage, hobbyist written, perfect for beginners and intermediates.
